= Literal Blocks

Literal blocks output text exactly as entered, similar to listing blocks but with different formatting.

== Basic Literal Block

....
This is a literal block.
It preserves text exactly as written.
    Including indentation.
....

== Literal Block with Title

.Literal: Sample Text
....
This literal block has a title.
It can contain any text content.
....

== Literal Block with Special Characters

....
<HTML>
  <body>
    <p>Content</p>
  </body>
</HTML>
....

== Multiple Literal Blocks

....
First literal block
....

....
Second literal block
with different content
....

== Literal Block vs Listing Block

Literal blocks (....) and listing blocks (----) are similar but may have different styling in the output.

